1. install library on arduino IDE
    - Blynk
    - ESP32
    - TridentTD_LineNotify

2. blynk cloud
    - create blynk template
    - create datastreams virtual pin 0 int value between 0 - 1
    - create new device from template
    - setup widget button type switch datastreams choose V0

3. code config
    - blynk define (3 line) can get form device in blynk cloud
    - wifi from your own connection
    - Line token get from Line notify (on web)

4. arduino IDE tool config
    - Board "ESP32 Wrover Module"
    - Upload speed "115200"
    - Flash Frequency "80MHz"
    - Flash Mode "QIO"
    - Partition Scheme "Huge APP (3MB No OTA/1MB SPIFFS)"
    - Core Debug Level "None"
    - Port "(depend on your PC)"

5. connect the electric circuit

6. upload code
    - click upload on arduino IDE 
    - when finished remove wire GND and GPIO 0
    - click serial monitor on arduino IDE
    - press reset button on esp32
    - program will be run
    - done
